Fruitvale Station;;2013;;R;;Biography,Crime,Drama;;7.5;;Ryan Coogler;;Michael B. Jordan,Melonie Diaz,Octavia Spencer,Kevin Durand,Chad Michael Murray,Ahna O'Reilly,Ariana Neal,Keenan Coogler,Trestin George,Joey Oglesby,Michael James,Marjorie Crump-Shears,Destiny Ekwueme,Bianca Rodriguez III,Julian Keyes,Kenny Grimm,Tommy Wright,Jemal McNeil;;Fruitvale chronicles the final hours of the life of Oscar Grant, the youth who was shot and killed by a BART police officer on Jan. 1, 2009 after he and his friends were pulled off a train at Oakland's Fruitvale Station in connection with an alleged fight.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2334649/